Program: Free Thinking
Title: Social Identity and Belonging in Europe, Valuing the Arts
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b05304sh
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 25 Feb 2015
Philip Dodd looks at the value of the arts with the former Chief Scientific Advisor to the EU, biologist Anne Glover,and discusses the notion of belonging and social identity in Europe with Dutch author Tommy Wieringa, Hungarian film director Kornel Mondruczo and academics Eric Kaufmann and Vesna Popovski. These are the Names, Tommy Wieringa's novel is published in English White God directed Kornel Mondruczo is in cinemas in London and across the UK Producer: Harry Parker. Show less